        "setup": "In your own ApostropheCMS project, configure an API key in `modules/@apostrophecms/express/index.js` under the `apiKeys` option. The docs show an example like `apiKeys: { myTestKey: { role: 'admin' } }`. See [Authentication](https://apostrophecms.com/docs/reference/api/authentication.html) and [API Explorer](https://apostrophecms.com/docs/reference/api/api-explorer.html). This is project-defined rather than minted from a hosted developer console."
